name: .VIDEO File Extension
summary: Learn about .VIDEO files and view a list of programs that open them.

description: Video file created by aTube Catcher, a program used for downloading YouTube videos to the local computer; saves the raw video downloaded from YouTube; can be converted to various video formats such as .WMV, .AVI, .3G2, and .MP4.

content: VIDEO files are created when the aTube Catcher "Output profile" option is set to "No Conversion (Only get original file)."
NOTE: aTube Catcher can also download videos from several other online video streaming sites.
